---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About" description="A bit about me.">
  <section style="padding: 5rem 0 6rem;">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1 style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">About</h1>
      <div class="prose-content">
        <p>
          Hi! I'm a CS/engineering student with interests that range from machine learning
          research to web security to building things that feel good to use.
        </p>
        <p>
          Right now I'm working on <strong>adapTrunc</strong>, a project exploring whether
          we can use class separability as a proxy to find the optimal truncation depth in
          BERT-style models — the goal being faster inference without fine-tuning every layer.
        </p>
        <p>
          Outside of research, I spend time on security labs, building small web tools,
          and occasionally writing about what I'm learning here on the blog.
        </p>
        <h2>Links</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></li>
          <li><a href="mailto:you@example.com">Email</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
